    <item>
      <title>贝恩资本提高对富士软件的收购报价，与 KKR 争夺 43 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/bain-raises-offer-for-fuji-soft-extending-takeover-war-with-kkr</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝恩资本 (Bain Capital) 提高了对富士软件公司的报价，对这家日本软件公司的估值为 43 亿美元，此举将进一步加剧其与 KKR &amp; Co. 在日本蓬勃发展的收购市场上的罕见竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/bain-raises-offer-for-fuji-soft-extending-takeover-war-with-kkr</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 05:22:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国农业信贷银行首席执行官在意大利银行交易中扮演关键角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/credit-agricole-ceo-brassac-plays-a-key-role-in-unicredit-s-bid-for-banco-bpm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲利普·布拉萨克 (Philippe Brassac) 即将退休，但意大利的一系列银行业交易有可能让他作为法国农业信贷银行 (Credit Agricole SA) 首席执行官的地位陷入混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/credit-agricole-ceo-brassac-plays-a-key-role-in-unicredit-s-bid-for-banco-bpm</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本生命保险将以 80 亿美元收购 Resolution，进军全球市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/nippon-life-to-buy-resolution-in-japan-s-biggest-insurance-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本生命保险公司同意以约 82 亿美元收购 Resolution Life Group Holdings Ltd.，这是日本保险公司最大的一笔收购，该公司正寻求扩张海外业务，弥补国内日益减弱的增长前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/nippon-life-to-buy-resolution-in-japan-s-biggest-insurance-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 01:41:26 GMT</pubDate>
